<span id="freeTextContainer6883287613940940982">Steve Hendricks is a freelance reporter. He is the author of <i>A Kidnapping in Milan</i> and <i>The Unquiet Grave: The FBI and the Struggle for the Soul of Indian Country</i>, which was named to several best-of-the-year lists in 2006. He lives in Tennessee and Montana.</span>

